{"word":"G1494 - εἰδωλόθυτον - eidōlóthyton - i-do-loth'-oo-ton - Offered to idols","slug":"G1494","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">εἰδωλόθυτον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>eidōlóthyton"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>i-do-loth'-oo-ton"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Offered to idols"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x0313;&#x03B4;&#x03C9;&#x03BB;&#x03BF;&#x0301;&#x03B8;&#x03C5;&#x03C4;&#x03BF;&#x03BD; - eido&#x0304;lothuton</b> - <i>i-do-loth'-oo-ton</i><p/>Neuter of a compound of <a href=\"#/G1497\">G1497</a> and a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G2380\">G2380</a>; an <i>image sacrifice</i>, that is, part of an <i>idolatrous offering:</i> - (meat, thing that is) offered (in sacrifice, sacrificed) to (unto) idols."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2405\">G2405</a>, <a href=\"#/G2406\">G2406</a>, <a href=\"#/G2407\">G2407</a>, <a href=\"#/G2409\">G2409</a>, <a href=\"#/G2411\">G2411</a>, <a href=\"#/G2412\">G2412</a>, <a href=\"#/G2413\">G2413</a>, <a href=\"#/G2416\">G2416</a>, <a href=\"#/G2417\">G2417</a>, <a href=\"#/G2418\">G2418</a>, <a href=\"#/G2420\">G2420</a>, <a href=\"#/G749\">G749</a>"}]}